Introduction

API do sistema de Almoxarifado

This documentation aims to provide all the information you need to work with our API.

As you scroll, you'll see code examples for working with the API in different programming languages in the dark area to the right (or as part of the content on mobile). You can switch the language used with the tabs at the top right (or from the nav menu at the top left on mobile).

Base URL

http://10.30.17.8:8000

Authenticating requests

This API is not authenticated.

Autenticação

APIs para login e logout do sistema

Cria um novo usuário no sistema

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/cadastrar"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "phrjplxnblsljqdxhyzhcsskipffeqfbuyztcobejkvmnnxzwpivehejasjhadhwwkooiyrojepxbplginkerzolcaff",
    "email": "tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br",
    "password": "Teste!123"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/cadastrar'
payload = {
    "name": "phrjplxnblsljqdxhyzhcsskipffeqfbuyztcobejkvmnnxzwpivehejasjhadhwwkooiyrojepxbplginkerzolcaff",
    "email": "tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br",
    "password": "Teste!123"
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/cadastrar',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'name' => 'phrjplxnblsljqdxhyzhcsskipffeqfbuyztcobejkvmnnxzwpivehejasjhadhwwkooiyrojepxbplginkerzolcaff',
            'email' => 'tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br',
            'password' => 'Teste!123',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (200):


{
    "data": {
        "name": "Teste Silva",
        "email": "teste@prefeitura.sp.gov.br",
        "updated_at": "2022-05-20T16:00:22.000000Z",
        "created_at": "2022-05-20T16:00:22.000000Z",
        "id": 2
    },
    "access_token": "3|LWV2yqNvqdIztktLYlvKehKMFn4aCOvKWc7xqMGf",
    "token_type": "Bearer"
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

POST api/cadastrar

Body Parameters

name  string  

Must not be greater than 255 characters.

email  string  

E-mail corporativo do usuário.

password  string  

Senha do usuário.

Efetua login no sistema

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/login"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "email": "tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br",
    "password": "Teste!123"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/login'
payload = {
    "email": "tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br",
    "password": "Teste!123"
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/login',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'email' => 'tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br',
            'password' => 'Teste!123',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (200):


{
    "message": "Oi username, bem-vindo!",
    "username": "username",
    "id": 1,
    "access_token": "1|IEXWeQ8KFQCu3d3giZbTJ7dOTNf9dSACPypztMB3",
    "token_type": "Bearer",
    "departamentos": {
        "3": "CGPABI",
        "4": "CGPABI/DIPO",
        "5": "CGPABI/DFS",
    }
}

Example response (401):


{
    "message": "E-mail ou senha está incorreto"
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

POST api/login

Body Parameters

email  string  

E-mail corporativo do usuário.

password  string  

Senha do usuário.

Altera a senha do usuário

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/alterar_senha"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer 5|02KLXZaRYzgJybyy2rMTRKXKIOuuE3EylnT7JQVv",
};

let body = {
    "email": "tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br",
    "password": "Teste!123",
    "newpassword": "Teste!456",
    "password_confirmation": "Teste!456"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/alterar_senha'
payload = {
    "email": "tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br",
    "password": "Teste!123",
    "newpassword": "Teste!456",
    "password_confirmation": "Teste!456"
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json',
  'Authorization': 'Bearer 5|02KLXZaRYzgJybyy2rMTRKXKIOuuE3EylnT7JQVv'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/alterar_senha',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
            'Authorization' => 'Bearer 5|02KLXZaRYzgJybyy2rMTRKXKIOuuE3EylnT7JQVv',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'email' => 'tisvma@prefeitura.sp.gov.br',
            'password' => 'Teste!123',
            'newpassword' => 'Teste!456',
            'password_confirmation' => 'Teste!456',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (200):


{
    "message": "Senha alterada com sucesso!"
}

Example response (401):


{
    "message": "Unauthenticated."
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

POST api/alterar_senha

Body Parameters

email  string  

E-mail corporativo do usuário.

password  string  

Senha atual do usuário.

newpassword  string  

Senha nova do usuário.

password_confirmation  string  

Confirmação de nova senha do usuário.

Departamento

APIs para listar, cadastrar, editar e remover dados de departamento

Lista os departamentos

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/departamentos"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/departamentos'
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('GET', url, headers=headers)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/departamentos',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "message": "Unauthenticated."
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

    headers,

    'http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia_itens/ea',

    ]
);

print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (200):


{
    "mensagem": "Item de transferencia encontrado com sucesso!",

        "entrada_id": 244,
        "item_id": 9,
        "quantidade": 4,
        "created_at": "2023-05-05T15:20:08.000000Z",
        "updated_at": "2023-05-05T15:22:01.000000Z"
    }
}

Example response (404):


{
    "mensagem": "Item de transferencia não encontrada!"
}

Request      

GET api/transferencia_itens/{id}

URL Parameters

id  string  

The ID of the transferencia iten.

integer  string optional  

ID do item.

Cadastra um item de transferencia

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia_itens"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "entrada_id": 1,
    "item_id": 5,
    "quantidade": 1
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia_itens'
payload = {
    "entrada_id": 1,
    "item_id": 5,
    "quantidade": 1
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia_itens',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'entrada_id' => 1,
            'item_id' => 5,
            'quantidade' => 1,
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (200):


{
    "mensagem": "Item de transferencia cadastrado com sucesso!",
    "itens": {
        "entrada_id": 1,
        "item_id": 5,
        "quantidade": 1,
        "updated_at": "2023-05-10T14:37:52.000000Z",
        "created_at": "2023-05-10T14:37:52.000000Z",
        "id": 4
    }
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

POST api/transferencia_itens

Body Parameters

entrada_id  integer  

ID da entrada.

item_id  integer  

ID do item transferencia.

quantidade  integer  

Quantidade de itens.

Deleta um Item de Transferencia

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia_itens/similique"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "DELETE",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia_itens/similique'
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('DELETE', url, headers=headers)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->delete(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia_itens/similique',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (200):


{
    "mensagem": "Item de transferencia deletado com sucesso!",
    "itens": {
        "id": 6,
        "entrada_id": 5,
        "item_id": 19,
        "quantidade": 2,
        "created_at": "2023-05-10T14:43:16.000000Z",
        "updated_at": "2023-05-10T14:43:16.000000Z"
    }
}

Example response (404):


{
    "mensagem": "Item de transferencia não encontrado para deletar."
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

GET api/ocorrencia_itens/{id}

URL Parameters

id  string  

The ID of the ocorrencia iten.

integer  string  

ID do item que deseja mostrar.

Cadastra um Item de Ocorrencia.

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/ocorrencia_itens"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "ocorrencia_id": 5,
    "item_id": 6,
    "quantidade": 36
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/ocorrencia_itens'
payload = {
    "ocorrencia_id": 5,
    "item_id": 6,
    "quantidade": 36
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/ocorrencia_itens',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'ocorrencia_id' => 5,
            'item_id' => 6,
            'quantidade' => 36,
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example response (200):


{
    "mensagem": "Item de ocorrencia cadastrado com sucesso!",

Entrada

APIs para listar, cadastrar, editar e remover dados de entrada

Lista as entradas

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/entradas"
);

const params = {
    "filter[processo_sei]": "6000.2022/0000123-4",
    "filter[numero_contrato]": "001/SVMA/2022",
    "filter[local]": "Base Leopoldina",
    "filter[numero_nota_fiscal]": "1234567",
    "filter[entrada_depois_de]": "2023-01-01",
    "filter[entrada_antes_de]": "2023-12-31",
    "filter[tipo]": "alvenaria",
    "sort": "-processo_sei",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/entradas'
params = {
  'filter[processo_sei]': '6000.2022/0000123-4',
  'filter[numero_contrato]': '001/SVMA/2022',
  'filter[local]': 'Base Leopoldina',
  'filter[numero_nota_fiscal]': '1234567',
  'filter[entrada_depois_de]': '2023-01-01',
  'filter[entrada_antes_de]': '2023-12-31',
  'filter[tipo]': 'alvenaria',
  'sort': '-processo_sei',
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('GET', url, headers=headers, params=params)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/entradas',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'filter[processo_sei]'=> '6000.2022/0000123-4',
            'filter[numero_contrato]'=> '001/SVMA/2022',
            'filter[local]'=> 'Base Leopoldina',
            'filter[numero_nota_fiscal]'=> '1234567',
            'filter[entrada_depois_de]'=> '2023-01-01',
            'filter[entrada_antes_de]'=> '2023-12-31',
            'filter[tipo]'=> 'alvenaria',
            'sort'=> '-processo_sei',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Request      

GET api/entradas

Query Parameters

filter[processo_sei]  string optional  

Filtro de número do processo.

filter[numero_contrato]  string optional  

Filtro de número do contrato da entrada

filter[local]  string optional  

Filtro de nome da base destino dos materiais da entrada.

filter[numero_nota_fiscal]  string optional  

Filtro do número da nota fiscal.

filter[entrada_depois_de]  string optional  

Filtro inicial de período da data de entrada do contrato.

filter[entrada_antes_de]  string optional  

Filtro final de período da data de entrada do contrato.

filter[tipo]  string optional  

Tipo de material da entrada.

sort  string optional  

Campo a ser ordenado (padrão ascendente, inserir um hífen antes para decrescente). Colunas possíveis: 'numero_nota_fiscal', 'data_entrada', 'processo_sei', 'numero_contrato', 'locais.nome', 'tipo_items.nome'

Cadastra uma nova entrada

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/entrada"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('departamento_id', '2');
body.append('local_id', '2');
body.append('processo_sei', '0123000134569000');
body.append('numero_contrato', '0001SVMA2022');
body.append('numero_nota_fiscal', '1234');
body.append('data_entrada', '"2022-08-11"');
body.append('entrada_items[][id]', '1');
body.append('entrada_items[][quantidade]', '500');
body.append('arquivo_nota_fiscal', document.querySelector('input[name="arquivo_nota_fiscal"]').files[0]);

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/entrada'
files = {
  'arquivo_nota_fiscal': open('C:\Users\x385830\AppData\Local\Temp\phpCFD1.tmp', 'rb')
}
payload = {
    "departamento_id": 2,
    "local_id": 2,
    "processo_sei": "0123000134569000",
    "numero_contrato": "0001SVMA2022",
    "numero_nota_fiscal": "1234",
    "data_entrada": "\"2022-08-11\"",
    "entrada_items": [
        {
            "id": 1,
            "quantidade": 500
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "quantidade": 480
        }
    ]
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, files=files, data=payload)
response.json()

$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/entrada',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'multipart/form-data',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'multipart' => [
            [
                'name' => 'departamento_id',
                'contents' => '2'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'local_id',
                'contents' => '2'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'processo_sei',
                'contents' => '0123000134569000'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'numero_contrato',
                'contents' => '0001SVMA2022'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'numero_nota_fiscal',
                'contents' => '1234'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'data_entrada',
                'contents' => '"2022-08-11"'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'entrada_items[][id]',
                'contents' => '1'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'entrada_items[][quantidade]',
                'contents' => '500'
            ],
            [
                'name' => 'arquivo_nota_fiscal',
                'contents' => fopen('C:\Users\x385830\AppData\Local\Temp\phpCFD1.tmp', 'r')
            ],
        ],
    ]
);

Edita um inventario

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/inventario/1"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "item_id": 2,
    "local_id": 2,
    "quantidade": 10,
    "departamento_id": 2,
    "qtd_alerta": 10
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "PUT",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/inventario/1'
payload = {
    "item_id": 2,
    "local_id": 2,
    "quantidade": 10,
    "departamento_id": 2,
    "qtd_alerta": 10
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('PUT', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->put(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/inventario/1',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'item_id' => 2,
            'local_id' => 2,
            'quantidade' => 10.0,
            'departamento_id' => 2,
            'qtd_alerta' => 10.0,
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/inventarios"
);

const params = {
    "filter[base]": "Leopoldina",
    "filter[item]": "Adaptador Pvc",
    "filter[tipo_item]": "alvenaria",
    "filter[tipo_medida]": "Pç",
    "filter[quantidade_maior_que]": "200",
    "filter[quantidade_menor_que]": "800",
    "sort": "-locais.nome",
};

    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

import json

  'filter[tipo_medida]': 'Pç',

  'filter[quantidade_menor_que]': '800',
  'sort': '-locais.nome',
}

            'filter[quantidade_maior_que]'=> '200',

Query Parameters

import json

  'Accept': 'application/json'

    'http://localhost:8000/api/ocorrencia/5',
    [

        ],
    ]
);

OrdemServico

APIs para listar, cadastrar, editar e remover dados de ordens de serviços

Cadastra uma ordem de serviço

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/ordem_servico"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "departamento_id": 2,
    "origem_id": 1,
    "local_servico_id": 2,
    "data_inicio_servico": "2022-08-30T14:48",
    "almoxarife_nome": "João",
    "almoxarife_email": "joao@teste.com.br",
    "user_id": 1,
    "status": "Iniciada",
    "data_fim_servico": "2022-08-31T17:50",
    "especificacao": "reforma",
    "profissional": "José",
    "horas_execucao": 10,
    "observacoes": "observações referente ao serviço"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

Lista as ordens de serviços

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/ordem_servicos"
);

const params = {
    "filter[origem]": "Leopoldina",
    "filter[local_servico]": "Ibirapuera",
    "filter[almoxarife_nome]": "Fulano",
    "filter[almoxarife_email]": "fulano@mail.com",
    "filter[servico_depois_de]": "2023-01-01",
    "filter[servico_antes_de]": "2023-12-31",
    "sort": "-locais.nome",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/ordem_servicos'
params = {
  'filter[origem]': 'Leopoldina',
  'filter[local_servico]': 'Ibirapuera',
  'filter[almoxarife_nome]': 'Fulano',
  'filter[almoxarife_email]': 'fulano@mail.com',
  'filter[servico_depois_de]': '2023-01-01',
  'filter[servico_antes_de]': '2023-12-31',
  'sort': '-locais.nome',
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('GET', url, headers=headers, params=params)
response.json()

        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',

        ],
        'query' => [
            'filter[origem]'=> 'Leopoldina',
            'filter[local_servico]'=> 'Ibirapuera',
            'filter[almoxarife_nome]'=> 'Fulano',
            'filter[almoxarife_email]'=> 'fulano@mail.com',
            'filter[servico_depois_de]'=> '2023-01-01',

Emite a Baixa de uma ordem de serviço

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/ordem_servico/1/baixa"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "ordem_servico_items": [
        {
            "id": 2,
            "enviado": 60,
            "usado": 50,
            "retorno": 10
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "enviado": 5,
            "usado": 3,
            "retorno": 2
        }
    ]
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/ordem_servico/1/baixa'
payload = {
    "ordem_servico_items": [
        {
            "id": 2,
            "enviado": 60,
            "usado": 50,
            "retorno": 10
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "enviado": 5,
            "usado": 3,
            "retorno": 2
        }
    ]
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/ordem_servico/1/baixa',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => \Symfony\Component\VarExporter\Internal\Hydrator::hydrate(
            $o = [
                clone (($p = &\Symfony\Component\VarExporter\Internal\Registry::$prototypes)['stdClass'] ?? \Symfony\Component\VarExporter\Internal\Registry::p('stdClass')),
                clone $p['stdClass'],
            ],
            null,
            [
                'stdClass' => [
                    'id' => [
                        2,
                        3,
                    ],
                    'enviado' => [
                        60,
                        5,
                    ],
                    'usado' => [
                        50,
                        3,
                    ],
                    'retorno' => [
                        10,
                        2,
                    ],
                ],
            ],
            [
                'ordem_servico_items' => [
                    $o[0],
                    $o[1],
                ],
            ],
            []
        ),
    ]
);

Profissional

APIs para listar, cadastrar, editar e remover dados de profissionais

Lista os profissionais de acordo com o local e departamento especificados

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/profissionais"
);

const params = {
    "local": "2",
    "depto": "3",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/profissionais'
params = {
  'local': '2',
  'depto': '3',
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('GET', url, headers=headers, params=params)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/profissionais',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'local'=> '2',
            'depto'=> '3',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/transferencia"
);

    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "base_origem_id": 2,
    "base_destino_id": 1,
    "data_transferencia": "2023\/05\/05",
    "itens": [
        {
            "item_id": 5,
            "quantidade": 355
        }

    "observacao": "Está faltando um parafuso",
    "observacao_motivo": "itens_faltando"
};

    method: "POST",

}).then(response => response.json());

import json

            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'base_origem_id' => 1,
            'base_destino_id' => 2,
            'data_transferencia' => '2023/05/05',
            'status' => 'recebido',
            'observacao' => 'Está faltando um parafuso',
            'observacao_motivo' => 'avaria',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

POST api/transferencia/{id}

URL Parameters

ID da transferencia.

Body Parameters

base_origem_id  integer  

ID do Local que sairá.

base_destino_id  integer  

ID do Local destino.

data_transferencia  date  

Data da Transferencia.

status  enum  

Status da transferencia (enviado, recebido, recusado).

observacao  text optional  

Observação.

observacao_motivo  enum optional  

Observação Motivo (nao_enviado, itens_faltando, extravio, furto, avaria).

Realiza a transferencia de materiais

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/transferir_itens/199"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "status": "enviado"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost:8000/api/transferir_itens/199'
payload = {
    "status": "enviado"
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, json=payload)
response.json()
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost:8000/api/transferir_itens/199',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'status' => 'enviado',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
